<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    background-color: #f2f2f2;
}

.container_hh {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.header_hh {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

h1 {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin: 20px 0;
}

h2 {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin: 20px 0 10px;
}

h3 {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

p {
    color: #555;
}

ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 20px;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    background-color: #f2f2f2;
}

    </style>
    <title>Customer Service</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header_hh">
        <h1>Customer Service</h1>
        </div>
    
    <div class="container_hh">
        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback, you can reach out to our customer service team using the following contact information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:customerservice@example.com">customerservice@example.com</a></li>
            <li>Phone: 1-800-123-4567</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <h3>1. How can I place an order?</h3>
        <p>To place an order, simply browse our website, select the items you want to purchase, and proceed to the checkout page. Follow the instructions to provide your shipping information and complete the payment.</p>
        
        <h3>2. What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
        <p>We accept major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express) and PayPal for online payments.</p>
        
        <h3>3. How long does shipping take?</h3>
        <p>The shipping time depends on your location and the shipping method chosen at checkout. We provide estimated delivery times during the checkout process.</p>
        
        <h3>4. What is your return policy?</h3>
        <p>We have a 30-day return policy. If you're not satisfied with your purchase, you can return it within 30 days of receiving the item for a refund or exchange. Please refer to our <a href="privacy-policy.html">Return Policy</a> for more details.</p>
        
        <h3>5. How can I track my order?</h3>
        <p>Once your order is shipped, we will provide you with a tracking number and a link to track your package on our website or the shipping carrier's website.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
